"title": "9140: last days",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "9140",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The final epoch of history which is marked by the coming of the Messiah and the establishment of God's kingdom. In the NT it is portrayed as the period between Jesus Christ's first coming and the consummation of all things at his return, and is marked by godlessness and the persecution of God's people.</p>\n<h2>OT expectation of the last days</h2>\n<h3>The Messianic kingdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:2-Isa2:4\">ISA 2:2–2:4</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:1-Mic4:3\">MIC 4:1–4:3</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:6-Isa9:7\">ISA 9:6–9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:1-Isa11:9\">ISA 11:1–11:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:20-Isa65:25\">ISA 65:20–65:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:15\">JER 33:15</a></p>\n<h3>The restoration of Israel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:16\">JER 33:16</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos3:5\">HOS 3:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:9\">ISA 25:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:9\">JER 30:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:4\">JER 50:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:1\">JOL 3:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:23\">ZEC 8:23</a></p>\n<h3>The day of the LORD</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:6-Isa13:12\">ISA 13:6–13:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek30:3\">EZK 30:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:11\">JOL 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:30-Joel2:31\">JOL 2:30–2:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:18-Amos5:20\">AMO 5:18–5:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:19-Acts2:20\">ACT 2:19–2:20</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's coming introduces the last days</h2>\n<h3>The timing of his revelation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:20\">1PE 1:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:4-Gal4:5\">GAL 4:4–4:5</a></p>\n<h3>The announcement of God's kingdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:15\">MRK 1:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:28\">MAT 12:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:20\">LUK 11:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:43\">LUK 4:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:1\">LUK 8:1</a></p>\n<h3>The fulfilment of Messianic promise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18-Luke4:21\">LUK 4:18–4:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1-Isa61:2\">ISA 61:1–61:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:4-Matt11:5\">MAT 11:4–11:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:22\">LUK 7:22</a></p>\n<h3>The outpouring of the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:16-Acts2:18\">ACT 2:16–2:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:28-Joel2:29\">JOL 2:28–2:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:27\">EZK 36:27</a></p>\n<h2>Revelation in the last days</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:1-Heb1:2\">HEB 1:1–1:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:16-Matt13:17\">MAT 13:16–13:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:23-Luke10:24\">LUK 10:23–10:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:25-Rom16:26\">ROM 16:25–16:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:9\">EPH 3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:26\">COL 1:26</a></p>\n<h2>Redemption in the last days</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:26\">HEB 9:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:24\">DAN 9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:21\">ACT 2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:32\">JOL 2:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:2\">2CO 6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:8\">ISA 49:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:18-1Pet1:20\">1PE 1:18–1:20</a></p>\n<h2>Features of the last days</h2>\n<h3>Godlessness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:1-2Tim3:5\">2TI 3:1–3:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:10\">DAN 12:10</a></p>\n<h3>Deception and apostasy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:1\">1TI 4:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:4-Matt24:5\">MAT 24:4–24:5</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:5\">MRK 13:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:8\">LUK 21:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:10-Matt24:12\">MAT 24:10–24:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:18-1John2:19\">1JN 2:18–2:19</a></p>\n<h3>Scoffing</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:3-2Pet3:4\">2PE 3:3–3:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:18-Jude1:19\">JUD 1:18–1:19</a></p>\n<h3>Persecution</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:33-Dan11:35\">DAN 11:33–11:35</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:30\">MRK 10:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:12-Luke21:17\">LUK 21:12–21:17</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:9-Matt24:10\">MAT 24:9–24:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:9-Mark13:13\">MRK 13:9–13:13</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's return brings the last days to a close</h2>\n<h3>It ushers in a new era</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:28\">HEB 9:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:49\">MAT 13:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:3\">MAT 24:3</a></p>\n<h3>It is identified with the day of the LORD</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:14\">2CO 1:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:2\">1TH 5:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:10\">2PE 3:10</a></p>\n<h2>Living in the last days</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:5\">HEB 6:5</a></strong> <em>Between Jesus Christ's comings, believers have a foretaste of the age to come.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:19-Eph1:21\">EPH 1:19–1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:1-Col3:4\">COL 3:1–3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:24-Heb10:25\">HEB 10:24–10:25</a></p>",
